fragment_downloaded_cb({"url":"FAQ.html#why-do-all-outputs-go-to-the-build-directory-that-corresponds-to-the-source-directory-in-which-they-are-declared","fragment":"Why do all outputs go to the build directory that corresponds to the source directory in which they are declared?\nThis simplifies debugging build problems, since you always know that files in\nbuild directory X must come from the corresponding source directory X.\n"});